                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "24b5f8d6-ca7e-49ad-9bab-2287ad7e2725",
                            "text": "Ask About the Letter",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "408582a6-bc7f-4d09-a495-2bd1b55521f9",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "0661a2f7-5493-46d9-ab58-6e9bff9a5f30",
                                    "text": "How did the letter get here?",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f6863a99-cd9f-4e29-9f88-7c863a55bc22",
                                    "actorId": "0661a2f7-5493-46d9-ab58-6e9bff9a5f30",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I guess the staff must have left it, it was there when I came in. I've never gotten mail from my family, so I don't know.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "c46883f0-3368-48f6-8f90-76db7559b577",
                            "text": "Get to Know Aeolus",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f2ad134d-6816-4ce6-9074-61193a836201",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "0661a2f7-5493-46d9-ab58-6e9bff9a5f30",
                                    "text": "So how did you find out about this school?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3095cfc7-76a4-4db6-b027-7bbf350666dc",
                                    "actorId": "0661a2f7-5493-46d9-ab58-6e9bff9a5f30",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "My father is a scribe for the Prince of Sardonia. He was in charge of writing the writ to permit the Hero University to open here.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "fada71c5-4da3-400d-b98c-84933dbaf974",
                                    "actorId": "0661a2f7-5493-46d9-ab58-6e9bff9a5f30",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "When Father saw that the university had a school for bards, he thought it was a great idea to send me away to the far side of Sardonia. It got me out of the house.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3903ca94-85e1-4672-ac1c-2a9c31d3ae43",
                                    "actorId": "0661a2f7-5493-46d9-ab58-6e9bff9a5f30",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Here, I get to study under Maestro Lorenzo, learn music, play instruments, and make friends. It's great.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "aa786e4e-bd6a-4fe0-8c49-bbc5b8ada461",
                                    "actorId": "0661a2f7-5493-46d9-ab58-6e9bff9a5f30",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "So what about you - what brought you here?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b53aa4db-5be6-4ec5-afa1-42e6ae5da806",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "0661a2f7-5493-46d9-ab58-6e9bff9a5f30",
                                    "text": "Let's just say that someone made me an offer that I couldn't refuse.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "3230955c-ac21-4159-aa9a-0c134f016a67",
                                    "actorId": "0661a2f7-5493-46d9-ab58-6e9bff9a5f30",
                                    "amount": "1",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "8be36f32-e84e-41e2-9440-991d5c41e0e4",
                            "text": "Tell Aeolus to Clean the Room",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                    "id": "dc4c27f7-5840-4b36-a1cb-07a5dd000410",
                                    "options": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "2531c0f9-b00a-428a-9738-c744296027bf",
                                            "text": "Be Polite",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "2d3ed6fd-9a67-4627-b48b-16ad4584dbac",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "0661a2f7-5493-46d9-ab58-6e9bff9a5f30",
                                                    "text": "It would be nice if you could clean up the piles of junk in this room so that I can move around without tripping over things.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
